00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,560
She's not a dummy.

861
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:34,960
Then did you find out?

862
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:38,080
They've already blew out their light.

863
00:40:38,640 --> 00:40:40,000
It's not convenient for me to go.

864
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,120
Go!

865
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:45,640
Right away.

866
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:08,200
Marquis still hasn't gone to bed?

867
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:11,280
There's no word from inside the room though.

868
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,360
My Big Madam

869
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,200
is very well.

870
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:15,320
She and I had honey cakes together

871
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,760
before she went to bed.

872
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:18,720
Is it good?

873
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:19,960
So good!

874
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:21,560
The chefs in our house

875
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:23,200
make them much better than outside.

876
00:41:24,240 --> 00:41:26,520
But the fried cherries.

877
00:41:26,520 --> 00:41:28,000
Ours isn't as good as the one from Nanbei Shop.

878
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:31,560
Tomorrow I'll go to the streets, to Nanbei Shop.

879
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:32,920
And I'll fetch some for you to eat.

880
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,320
Eat, eat, eat.

881
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:41,400
How do those two even look like

882
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:42,360
mistress and servant?

883
00:41:42,520 --> 00:41:44,000
They are like sisters!

884
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,400
Other than eating all day,

885
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,320
what else do they know?

886
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,120
What are you doing, Marquis?

887
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:04,840
She can blow out the candle to sleep

888
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,760
and so can I!

889
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,720
Blow out the light.

890
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:16,160
Marquis. Are we going back?

891
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:20,280
The Ox Hour is over?

892
00:43:21,680 --> 00:43:22,720
The clapper just went off.

893
00:43:26,560 --> 00:43:27,960
Looks like if I don't go back,

894
00:43:28,560 --> 00:43:30,480
she won't come and ask about me.
